That’s a pity.

84
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:36,920
I'm tied up today, and tomorrow's full of classes.

85
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,159
Was gonna bring some stuff over,

86
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,600
but forgot it all.

87
