Thought of bringing my laptop too.

88
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,440
Left it at home in the end.

89
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:01,200
Hey, stop it!

90
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,640
Not just my legs,

91
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,040
now my arms too?

92
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,840
Haven't I said I don't like that?

93
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:23,840
You know, today's been my happiest day.

94
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:28,280
You call me dramatic, yet you're the same.

95
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,280
Next time, skip the surprise, okay?

96
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:41,080
If you plan to visit, just tell me.

97
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:44,480
We'll find a nice place to eat together.

98
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:51,560
I came without expectations.

99
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:55,560
Just to see you like this.

100
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,200
Nick,

101
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,240
can I ask something?

102
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:08,760
Of course.

103
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:14,080
Do you treat me nicely just because my mom helped you out?

104
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:21,240
Partly, but not entirely.

105
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,080
Remember when Cham hit me?

106
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:26,480
I was ready to return your mom's money that day.

107
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:29,960
And to stop tutoring you.

108
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:37,159
Ah, I see...

109
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:41,640
Back then, I didn't want you to put up with me either.

110
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,880
I felt like a meteorite

111
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,680
constantly crashing into you.

112
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:52,360
But we should thank certain meteors that hit us.

113
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:59,040
Those wounds from that day,

114
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,240
they brought you back to study with me.

115
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:05,640
And who's calling you a black hole?

116
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,520
I think it's quite correct.

117
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:15,600
So this black hole thing, is it good or bad?

118
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:16,840
I'm confused now.

119
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:26,800
The real reason I'm here today is
because I want to confess something...

120
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:32,400
I haven't been calling you much lately

121
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,520
