122
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,400
But... he won’t stay for long.

123
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,800
Then why'd you let him move in?

124
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:47,320
You know Cham is good to me too

125
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:53,920
He dropped out of school and worked
to support me until I graduated.

126
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,840
Did he just ask for a place to stay?

127
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:01,000
He hasn't troubled you this time, right?

128
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:06,760
Can you promise not to tell your mom?

129
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:12,440
No, she's even more bipolar now.

130
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:19,320
If she finds out, she'll never let me live with you next year.

131
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,720
But here's my promise...

132
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,800
If we move in together,

133
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,640
I won't let Champ interfere with you.

134
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,520
But before next year,

135
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:39,200
