Champ, have you seen my laptop?

144
00:12:43,880 --> 00:12:46,280
Didn't you take it? I saw you with your bag.

145
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:51,520
I thought so, but it wasn't in there.

146
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:56,080
So, you think I took it?

147
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:58,480
Did you?

148
