150
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:14,880
Just tell me where, I'll get it back.

151
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:20,800
You have cash, huh?
Why not just lend it when I asked?

152
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,920
Do you even see me as your brother anymore?

153
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:29,320
And you? Do you still see me as your brother?

154
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,600
I paid for that laptop, remember?

155
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:35,480
Whether it's lost or sold, that's my call.

156
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,360
But it's mine.

157
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:39,520
Where'd you pawn it? Just tell me...

158
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,920
Tell me now!

159
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:54,160
Hey there!

160
