161
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:31,760
[T.O.D.: Yeah, just a small argument with mom.]

162
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:40,760
[Kun: Wanna study together over a call?]

163
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:47,120
[T.O.D.: I'm sleepy. See you tomorrow morning.]

164
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:54,320
[Kun: Remember to bring your dad’s cofee.]

165
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:58,640
