166
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:14,080
Why are you up so late, Tod?

167
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,920
Was waiting for you to get back.

168
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:24,360
Using your phone in the dark will ruin your eyes.

169
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:31,720
You could join mom in bed.

170
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:34,000
I’ll sleep on the sofa.

171
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,600
Sleeping down here will only hurt your back.

172
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,520
Better go to bed,

173
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:41,040
you've got school tomorrow.

174
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:52,840
Have you been busy lately? You're hardly home.

175
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:57,480
Always out early, home late.

176
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,960
Yeah, this job's harder than in Bangkok.

177
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:03,240
Tougher work, less pay.

178
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:10,920
So, has mom sold the house in Bangkok yet?

179
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,760
Not yet. I don't want to sell.

180
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:17,560
That's why I try to earn money to support us all.

181
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:22,680
Does this mean we may have to return to Bangkok?

182
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:26,200
Want to move back there?

183
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:32,720
Mom didn't tell you about my Thawiwat school exam?

184
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:37,160
Heard something about it. When's the test?

185
00:16:38,920 --> 00:16:40,160
Next month.

186
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:45,680
Just study but take it easy.

187
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:56,360
Could you talk to mom about it?

188
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:59,720
She seems against the idea.

189
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:03,000
Then let's drop the plan.

190
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:05,960
Seems like your mom doesn't want to go back to Bangkok.

191
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:09,560
I've tried convincing her several times,

192
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,640
doesn't look hopeful.

193
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:17,720
I'll get ready for a shower.

194
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:22,760
How about this?

195
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:26,079
You want to move in with Nick, right?

196
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,359
Maybe Nick can talk to her.

197
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:31,920
She might listen to him.

198
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:39,640
Thank you!

