203
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:34,800
Hello, Nick. Where did you disappear to?

204
00:18:35,560 --> 00:18:36,680
Tod...

205
00:18:38,080 --> 00:18:39,520
My mom, she passed away.

206
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:43,520
Sorry for not telling you...

207
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,120
I'm so sorry.

208
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:53,360
Why are you up so early, anyway?

209
00:18:54,360 --> 00:18:55,600
Where are you now?

210
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:58,880
In Chiang Mai. Just finished funeral prep.

211
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:04,560
I’ll ask my parents to take me to you.

212
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,320
No, don't bother.

213
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:09,720
It's only a three-day thing,

214
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:12,640
and I prefer keeping it low-key.

215
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,360
I might be busy for a while,

216
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:20,200
a lot of things to handle.

217
00:19:21,280 --> 00:19:23,440
You just focus on your studies,

218
00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:25,320
don't worry about me.

219
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:32,120
I want to be there to support you.

220
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:34,720
Don't come. It's a long way,

221
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:38,120
and tickets are pricey. Don't tell your parents.

222
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:40,440
I'll reach out after it's over.

223
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:44,400
But Nick, your mom just died. I should be there.

224
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:52,520
Nick, I really am sorry.

225
00:19:56,360 --> 00:19:58,800
Hello... Nick...

226
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:10,160
[Pluto: Sorry for hanging up.]

227
00:20:11,360 --> 00:20:15,600
[Pluto: We'll talk later.]

228
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:41,000
-I don’t know.
-How can I do this?

229
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:45,160
-It's simple. Can’t figure it out?
-Nope, I can’t.

230
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:48,840
