Don’t worry about pain, I have a gentle touch.

546
00:46:45,400 --> 00:46:46,880
Hold still!

547
00:46:55,280 --> 00:46:59,480
Tod, do you think the universe has an end?

548
00:47:02,280 --> 00:47:05,280
