553
00:47:26,720 --> 00:47:28,520
Is that the answer you were looking for?

554
00:47:31,480 --> 00:47:32,760
From what you've told me,

555
00:47:33,320 --> 00:47:35,560
this theory you once told me about

556
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:38,120
